Package: padnote
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qt 6 Linux text editor with syntax highlighting
 padnote-- is a Qt 6 text editor for Linux with multi-document tabs,
 split view, find/replace with regex, find-in-files, function list,
 document map, project panels, file browser, customisable themes,
 and user-defined languages. Syntax highlighting via Scintilla and
 Lexilla covers 80+ languages out of the box.
